title: Mindless Self Indulgence - If
description:
If is the fifth studio album by New York group Mindless Self Indulgence. It is due to be released through The End Records on April 29, 2008. Mindless Self Indulgence are planning a small North American tour in support of this album with The Birthday Massacre, followed by a world tour.
